name: ACEP63DenominatorExclusion
title: ACEP 63 Denominator exclusion
description: ACEP 63, Avoidance of Acute High-Risk Prescriptions in geriatric patients at discharge
purpose:
(Clinical Focus: Patients with any of the following discharge diagnosis:
-seizure disorder
-rapid eye movement sleep disorder
-ethanol withdrawal
-benzodiazepine withdrawal
-severe generalized anxiety disorder
-end-of-life care
-Allergic Reactions
-Dermatitis
-Vertigo
-Labyrinthitis
-ED Visit for Prescription Refill),(Data Element Scope: ),(Inclusion Criteria: ),(Exclusion Criteria: )
